{"tid":1993920,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE首部YouTube紀錄片今首播 6月1日推新曲回歸","createTime":"2020-04-29T06:23:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T14:03:03.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f23e732626078398b464ffad7684405ee0881d1b","tid":1993920,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T06:23:12.000Z","msg":"跟著TWICE紀錄歷史！<br />\n<br />\n人氣女團TWICE昨日全員出席影片社群平台YouTube的「 #StayHome and hang #WithMe」活動，並為她們首套YouTube原創紀錄片《TWICE: Seize the Light》首播發布造勢，紀錄片將於今晚（29日）韓國時間11點首播，共有8集。TWICE也是首個單獨出演此原創紀錄片系列的K-POP女子組合，在昨天的線上直播活動當中，她們亦透露正在籌備推出新歌，已定於6月1日發表為粉絲送上全新作品。<br />\n<br />\n《TWICE: Seize the Light》此原創紀錄片將展現組合從練習生時期到出道後光榮瞬間的歷史，並以組合在16個城市舉行25場演出的世界巡演《TWICE WORLD TOUR 2019 'TWICELIGHTS'》為故事背景，共製作了8集，將於今晚（29日）開始，每星期公開TWICE的成長記錄、世巡花絮等，結合團隊的開始、現在與未來的相關內容，並透過YouTube在全球81個地區播出。<br />\n<br />\nTWICE成員們昨日下午出席了線上直播發布會，當中也提及她們將於6月1日發表新曲《MORE N MORE》回歸，是團體繼去年9月推出的《Feel Special》後，時隔約9個月再發表新作品，成員表示目前錄音已經完成，MV亦已進行了拍攝：「現在就只剩下與ONCE見面了！」"},{"pid":"6483cb83a498a97a4d9f992b11b59ac9f6a749a2","tid":1993920,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T06:23:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/04/20200429_EN_TWICE_FB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F04%2F20200429_EN_TWICE_FB.jpg&h=d2f277ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"885df00062133111d21afb0a741478a631d051d5","tid":1993920,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T06:24:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/04/20200429_EN_TWICE3-e1588130226752.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F04%2F20200429_EN_TWICE3-e1588130226752.png&h=79cfac97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/upload